data.description: Welcome to East Garrison. This two-story, 3 bed, 3 full bath condo/townhouse features an open floor plan, spacious kitchen with large pantry and is equipped with energy saving stainless steel appliances featuring a 5 burner gas stove. 2nd floor laundry located upstairs between 2 large bedrooms and bathrooms. Large ensuite master bedroom w/large walk-in closet. Small TV/den area is also located upstairs. Lots of storage and a 2 car garage! New custom blinds throughout, tankless water heater, water softener system.  Laminate hardwood downstairs and carpet upstairs. EG has its own fire dept. Well maintained grounds. Lincoln Park is used as a soccer field, dog park, and playground area and is directly across the street from the condo. Other playground, walking, and dog park areas are throughout the East Garrison community. Short driving distance to hiking/biking/rec trails, beaches, shopping, great wineries, or a quick drive to anywhere around the beautiful Monterey Peninsula.
